          <h1><a href="why-retention-starts-in-the-driveway.html">Why Retention Starts in the Driveway: Lessons from CEO, Amit Chandarana</a></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <span> Written by <a class="author-link" href="author/curbee%3FhsLang=en.html">Curbee</a> | June 03, 2025 </span>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-section">
          <span><p><span><span><strong>Zero in on why retention is slipping and how mobile service can help fix it.</strong></span></span></p>

<p>On a recent episode of the <a href="https://www.podbean.com/ew/pb-x6wz5-18b8f80" rel="noopener"><em>Retention Roadmap</em> podcast</a>, Curbee CEO <a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/amitchandarana1&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjxm_u9xtWNAxWTAHkGHX1HJqEQFnoECBgQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw21cbCPEV8vTG2VD04gbAZ7" rel="noopener">Amit Chandarana</a> joined host <a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/billspringerdrivesure&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjuyOHQxtWNAxVRm4kEHacZNZEQFnoECCAQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw1GNa1Yvk-f8k8fwwTQdS33" rel="noopener">Bill Springer</a> for a deep dive into the future of mobile service. With more than 30,000 at-home appointments completed and partnerships with OEMs like Stellantis, Amit brought more than just data. He laid out a clear plan for how dealerships can turn mobile service into a powerful tool for retention and revenue.</p>
<div class="hs-cta-embed hs-cta-simple-placeholder hs-cta-embed-190970638912">
